{# Marp slide-source template for anvil:deck.
   Slides are separated by `---` on its own line.
   Speaker notes can be embedded inline as HTML comments matching `<!-- speaker: ... -->`
   (Marp's native presenter-notes mechanism). A parallel speaker-notes.md is also produced
   by deck-draft for ease of human editing.

   Required Marp frontmatter:
     marp: true             — enables Marp processing
     theme: anvil-deck      — references the shipped theme in assets/anvil-deck.css
     paginate: true         — page numbers on every slide except title
     size: 16:9             — investor-standard aspect ratio
     math: mathjax          — Marp v3 default math engine; covers more LaTeX than KaTeX
     html: true             — passes raw HTML/<script> through (does NOT render inline ```mermaid as diagrams in the PDF — issue #65; render diagrams to PNG via mmdc)

   The math + html pins are also set at the CLI level via
   anvil/lib/marp/config.yml (consumed with `marp --config-file ...`); pinning
   them here keeps deck.md self-describing so it renders correctly even when
   that config file is not on the CLI line.
#}
---
marp: true
theme: anvil-deck
paginate: true
size: 16:9
math: mathjax
html: true
---

